<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .instructions { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50; }
        .important { color: #e74c3c; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background: #4CAF50; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Your Meeting is Confirmed</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear Client,</p>
        <p>Your counseling session has been confirmed for:</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= meetingDate %><br>
           <strong>Time:</strong> <%= meetingTime %><br>
           <strong>Type:</strong> <%= meetingType %></p>


        <div class="instructions">
            <h3>Important Instructions:</h3>
            <%- instructions.split('\n').map(line => `<p>${line}</p>`).join('') %>
        </div>

        <p class="important">Please note: Your privacy and confidentiality are our top priority. You will appear as "Anonymous Client" during the session.</p>

        <p>If you need to cancel or reschedule, please do so at least 12 hours in advance.</p>

        <p>For support, contact us at support@micounselor.com</p>

        <p>We look forward to supporting you.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>